@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@authToken = {{auth_token}}

### Upload Pet Photo (Cloudinary)
### Use an HTTP client that supports file uploads (e.g. VS Code REST Client or Thunder Client).
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image?folder=pets
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=BOUNDARY

--BOUNDARY
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="pet.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./samples/pet.jpg
--BOUNDARY--

###
### Upload Boarding Profile Photo
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image?folder=boarding
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=BOUNDARY

--BOUNDARY
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="boarding1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./samples/boarding1.jpg
--BOUNDARY--

###
### Upload Document (Vaccination Record as Image/PDF)
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image?folder=documents
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=BOUNDARY

--BOUNDARY
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="vaccination-card.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./samples/vaccination-card.jpg
--BOUNDARY--

